    h3 A Hire Quote includes:
    ul
      li A list of vehicle models and when they are required.
      li Information about delivering and collecting the vehicle.
      li Add-ons selected for each vehicle model and the cost involved.
      li Customisable fees associated with each vehicle model. 
      li References to vehicle model brochures and photos.
      li References to Add-on brochures and photos (not yet available).

  section
    h3 How to prepare a Hire Quote
    p It is assumed that the following items have already been defined:
    p.indent  
      span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok 
      |  Vehicle Models 
      span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok 
      |  Hire Add-ons 
      span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok 
      |  Hire Fee Types 
      span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok 
      |  Brochures and photos that should accompany the quotes
    p Create a Hire Quote. There are 3 ways to do this:
    ul 
      li The Hire Quotes List (https://secure.bus4x4.com.au/hire_quotes)
      li The Quick Links on the left of the page
      li Open the enquiry from the desired customer, provide all missing details and click on the Create Hire Quote button.
    p Add vehicle model to the quote. 
    ul 
      li Define the Hire arrangements for each included vehicle model according to the preferences of the customer.
      li Change the associated fees if necessary.
      li Choose add-ons for the quoted vehicles, if required. 
      li Review the content and send the completed quote to the customer.

